data.description: Spacious home in a great neighborhood! Centrally located to Marine bases, shopping & medical offices. This .44 acre lot is completely fenced & has a large shed with electricity that is currently used as a workshop plus another storage shed. The gardens throughout the yard were designed & lovingly maintained by the current owners. There are many varieties of plants and flowers to attract the bees and butterflies and will give you endless hours of enjoyment sitting under the canopy of trees. This home has had many upgrades such as luxury vinyl flooring throughout the main living areas, updated kitchen and baths and new HVAC just two years ago.
